ac \ucd9c\uc5f0 '\ub098\ub9cc \uc5c6\uc5b4 \uace0\uc591\uc774', \ub7f0\uce6d \ud3ec\uc2a4\ud130 \uacf5\uac1c |url=http://mbnmoney.mbn.co.kr/news/view?news_no=MM1003655162 |access-date=August 8, 2019 |work=MBN |date=July 16, 2019 |language=ko}}</ref> on December 3, 2019, he has been awarded as \"Person of the Year\" award at 2019 COSMO Glam Night, one of the most prestigious awards in China.<ref name=\":60\">{{cite news|url=https://www.sedaily.com/NewsView/1VRXZM4LCA|title=\uae40\ud76c\ucca0, \u4e2d \ucf54\uc2a4\ubaa8\ud3f4\ub9ac\ud0c4 \uc8fc\uad00 \uc2dc\uc0c1\uc2dd\uc11c '\uc62c\ud574\uc758 \uc778\ubb3c' \uc120\uc815|date=December 4, 2019|access-date=December 4, 2019}}</ref> Heechul and ''Knowing Bros'' co-star [[Lee Soo-geun]] collaborated as the project group Woojoo Jjokkomi, and released a cover of Mr. 2's \"White Winter\" for [[SM Station discography#2019: SM Station X 4 LOVEs for Winter|SM Station X 4 LOVEs for Winter]] project.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2019/12/12/2019121201123.html|title=[\uacf5\uc2dd] \uae40\ud76c\ucca0X\uc774\uc218\uadfc '\uc6b0\uc8fc\ucabc\uaf2c\ubbf8', 15\uc77c '\ud558\uc580\uaca8\uc6b8' \uacf5\uac1c\u2026ITZY \uc9c0\uc6d0\uc0ac\uaca9\ucd9c\ucc98|date=December 12, 2019|access-date=December 12, 2019}}</ref>\n\nIn 2020, following a successful year, Heechul continue his TV personalities career with appearing in ''[[Studio Music Hall]]''<ref>{{Cite news |script-title=ko:\uae40\ud76c\ucca0X\uae40\uc774\ub098X\ubc30\uc21c\ud0c1 '\uc2a4\ud29c\ub514\uc624 \uc74c\uc545\ub2f9' Mnet \ud3b8\uc131 \ud655\uc815\u202621\uc77c \uccab\ubc29\uc1a1|url=https://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2020/01/20/2020012001230.html|accessdate=January 20, 2020|language=ko}}</ref>, ''[[Love of 7.7 Billion]]''<ref name=\":64\" >{{Cite news |script-title=ko:\uc2e0\ub3d9\uc5fdX\uc720\uc778\ub098X\uae40\ud76c\ucca0 \u201877\uc5b5\uc758 \uc0ac\ub791\u2019 MC \ucd9c\uaca9\u2026\uad6d\uacbd \uc5c6\ub294 \uc0ac\ub791 \uc774\uc57c\uae30 \ud3bc\uce5c\ub2e4|url=http://m.mbn.co.kr/news/4029725|accessdate=January 9, 2020|language=ko}}</ref>, ''[[20th Century Hit Song]]''<ref name=\":65\" >{{Cite news |script-title=ko:\uae40\ubbfc\uc544 MC\ubc1c\ud0c1, \uae40\ud76c\ucca0\uacfc '\uc774\uc2ed\uc138\uae30 \ud79b-\ud2b8\uc3ed' \ucd9c\uc5f0|url=http://www.busan.com/view/busan/view.php?code=2020030611240348018|accessdate=March 6, 2020|language=ko}}</ref><ref name=\":66\" >{{Cite news |script-title=ko:'\uc6cc\ud06c\ub9e8' \uae40\ubbfc\uc544 \uae30\uc0c1\uce90\uc2a4\ud130, \uae40\ud76c\ucca0\uacfc '\uc774\uc2ed\uc138\uae30 \ud79b-\ud2b8\uc3ed' MC \ubc1c\ud0c1\u202627\uc77c \uccab \ubc29\uc1a1|url=https://www.msn.com/ko-kr/entertainment/news/\uc6cc\ud06c\ub9e8-\uae40\ubbfc\uc544-\uae30\uc0c1\uce90\uc2a4\ud130-\uae40\ud76c\ucca0\uacfc-\uc774\uc2ed\uc138\uae30-\ud79b-\ud2b8\uc3ed-mc-\ubc1c\ud0c1\u202627\uc77c-\uccab-\ubc29\uc1a1/ar-BB10Om4m|accessdate=March 6, 2020|language=ko}}</ref> and ''High School Style Icon''.\n\n== Artistry ==\nHeechul production discography is predominately [[Rock music]], proving his love for traditional Korean style rock.<ref>{{cite web|title=\uae40\ud76c\ucca0, 24\uc77c \uccab \uc194\ub85c \uc2f1\uae00 '\uc61b\ub0a0\uc0ac\ub78c' \ubc1c\ud45c|url=http://www.sportalkorea.com/butterfly/view.php?gisa_uniq=201904171013773153&key=&field=&section_code=B1000&search_key=y|website=Sportal Korea|accessdate=February 20, 2020}}</ref> He admitted that, he had a dream about a rock band when he was a teenager and a trainee.<ref>{{cite web|title=\"\ub354\uc774\uc0c1 \ucda4 \ucd9c \uc218 \uc5c6\uc5b4\"\u2026\ub370\ubdd4 15\ub144 \ucc28 \uac00\uc218 \uae40\ud76c\ucca0\uc758 \uace0\ubbfc|url=https://www.edaily.co.kr/news/read?newsId=01148006622717208&mediaCodeNo=258|website=E Daily|accessdate=February 20, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='\ubcf5\uba74\uac00\uc655' \uae40\ud76c\ucca0 \"\uad50\ud1b5\uc0ac\uace0 \ud6c4 \uc624\ub79c\ub9cc\uc5d0 \ubb34\ub300...\ub108\ubb34 \ud589\ubcf5\ud588\ub2e4\"|url=https://www.ytn.co.kr/_sn/0117_202002171135411974|website=YTN|accessdate=February 20, 2020}}</ref>\n\nHeechul is active as a lyricist and has written several of Super Junior's music, including \"[[Show Me Your Love (TVXQ and Super Junior song)|Show Me Your Love]]\", \"[[Oops! (Super Junior song)|Oops]]\", and \"[[Lo Siento (Super Junior song)|Lo Siento]]\".<ref name=\":23\" /> Moreover, he has written lyrics for his project group [[Kim Heechul & Kim Jungmo]]'s \"I Wish\", \"Narcissus\", and \"Ulsanbawi\", as well as \"[[Sweet Dream (2016 song)|Sweet Dream]]\" for Universe Cowards, which achieve an \"all-kill\" by topping the music charts.<ref name=\":23\" /><ref name=\":46\" /> In addition, he wrote the lyrics for [[Orange Caramel]]'s \"[[Lipstick (Orange Caramel album)|Shanghai Romance]]\", which peaked at number eight on the Gaon Digital Chart.<ref name=\":12\" >{{cite web|title=Shanghai Romance|url=http://www.melon.com/album/detail.htm?albumId=2019316|website=[[Melon (online music service)|MelOn]]|publisher=LOEN Entertainment|accessdate=November 4, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008090730/http://www.melon.com/album/detail.htm?albumId=2019316|archive-date=October 8, 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n== Public image ==\n[[File:150715 \ud76c\ucca0.jpg|thumb|230x230px|left|{{small|Heechul - 10th Anniversary Special Album ''[[Devil (Super Junior album)|Devil]]'' Press Conference on July 15, 2015.}}]]\nHeechul is very popular for being a celebrity without any major scandals and model idol group member who never has rumors.<ref>{{cite news | title='\ud48d\ubb38\uc73c\ub85c\ub4e4\uc5c8\uc1fc' \uae40\ud76c\ucca0 \"\ub370\ubdd4 15\ub144\ucc28 \ub17c\ub780\u7121 \ubaa8\ubc94\uc5f0\uc608\uc778? \uc0ac\uc2e4 \uc774\uac8c \uc815\uc0c1\" | date=September 22, 2019 | url=http://www.nbnnews.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=319754#08r5 | accessdate=January 22, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title='\ub77c\ub514\uc624\uc2a4\ud0c0' \uae40\ud76c\ucca0 \"'\ubaa8\ubc94 \uc544\uc774\ub3cc' \uc218\uc2dd\uc5b4, \ub2f9\ud669\uc2a4\ub7ec\uc6cc\" | date=December 31, 2019 | url=https://www.mk.co.kr/star/hot-issues/view/2019/12/1098828/ | accessdate=January 6, 2020}}</ref> Also known for his unique personality, no-holds-barred attitude and wit \u2013 all of which has earned him spots on variety shows.<ref name=\":41\" /><ref name=\":40\">{{cite news | title=[\uc5f0\uc608\uc758 \ubc95\uce59] \uae40\ud76c\ucca0, \ud604\uc7ac \uac00\uc7a5 \ud3fc \uc88b\uc740 \uc608\ub2a5\uc778\u2026'\ubbf8\uccd0 \ub0a0\ub6f0\ub294 \uc911' | date=June 15, 2016 | work=Sports Donga | url=http://sports.donga.com/3/02/20160615/78675308/2 | accessdate=October 12, 2018 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005071919/http://sports.donga.com/3/02/20160615/78675308/2 | archive-date=October 5, 2018 | url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\":42\">{{cite news |title=[\uc5f0\uc608\uc758 \ubc95\uce59] \uae40\ud76c\ucca0, \ud604\uc7ac \uac00\uc7a5 \ud3fc \uc88b\uc740 \uc608\ub2a5\uc778\u2026'\ubbf8\uccd0 \ub0a0\ub6f0\ub294 \uc911'| date= June 15, 2016 | work=Naver| url=http://m.entertain.naver.com/read?aid=0000480890&oid=382& | accessdate=October 12, 2018}}</ref> Heechul's hosting received positive reviews. OSEN wrote: \"He is making an artistic character that has not only been able to cope with the excellent buzzword copying ability as well as the irreverent speech.\"<ref>{{cite news | title=[Oh!\uc388 \ucd08\uc810]\uae40\ud76c\ucca0, \uac15\ud638\ub3d9\u2192\uc2e0\ub3d9\uc5fd\u2192\uc774\uacbd\uaddc \uc12d\ub835\ud55c '\ub300\uc138 of \ub300\uc138' | date=June 3, 2017 | work=OSEN | url=http://www.osen.co.kr/article/G1110655335 | accessdate=October 27, 2018 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181027185859/http://www.osen.co.kr/article/G1110655335 | archive-date=October 27, 2018 | url-status=live }}</ref> KStar News wrote: \"His charm is make space for guest to shine.\"<ref name=\":41\">{{cite news | title=\uae40\ud76c\ucca0, \uc608\ub098 \uc9c0\uae08\uc774\ub098 '\ub