ews/132059 | archive-date=October 5, 2018 | url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=\uae40\ud76c\ucca0 \"\uc5f4\uc560\uc124 \ud130\uc9c8 \ub54c\ub9c8\ub2e4 \ub0b4\uac00 \ub9c8\ub2f4\ub69c? \uae30\ubd84 \ub098\ube60\" | date=May 17, 2017 | work=[[JoongAng Ilbo]] | url=http://m.entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0003537852 | accessdate=October 5, 2018 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005111820/https://m.entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0003537852 | archive-date=October 5, 2018 | url-status=live }}</ref> This became one of the reasons behind the rumors regarding his sexuality,<ref name=\":25\">{{cite news | title=\ud574\ud53c\ud22c\uac8c\ub3543' \uae40\ud76c\ucca0 \"\uc774\ub7f0 \ub9d0\ud558\uae30 \uadf8\ub807\uc9c0\ub9cc\" \uac8c\uc774\uc124 \uc785 \uc5f0\ub2e4 | date=March 15, 2017 | work=Sports Hankooki | url=http://sports.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201703/sp20170315141214136660.htm | accessdate=October 6, 2018 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005112359/http://sports.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201703/sp20170315141214136660.htm | archive-date=October 5, 2018 | url-status=live }}</ref> along with his androgynous appearance, especially with having a \"[[kkonminam|pretty boy]]\" look that coined him the nickname \"Prettier Than Female\", and cross-dressing.<ref>{{cite news | title=\"\uc800 \uc138\uc0c1 \ube44\uc8fc\uc5bc\"..\uc774\uc900\uae30\u2192\uc7a5\ub3d9\uc724, \uc5ec\uc790\ubcf4\ub2e4 \ub354 \uc608\uc05c '\uc5ec\uc7a5\ub0a8\uc7905'[Oh!\uc388 \ud0d0\uad6c] | date=October 2, 2010 | work=MSN |url=https://www.msn.com/ko-kr/entertainment/tv/\u201c\uc800-\uc138\uc0c1-\ube44\uc8fc\uc5bc\u201d\uc774\uc900\uae30\u2192\uc7a5\ub3d9\uc724-\uc5ec\uc790\ubcf4\ub2e4-\ub354-\uc608\uc05c-\u2018\uc5ec\uc7a5\ub0a8\uc7905\u2019oh\uc388-\ud0d0\uad6c/ar-AAI8uFU | accessdate=February 20, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| title=\uc5ec\uc790 \ubcf4\ub2e4 \ub354 \uc608\uc05c \ub0a8\uc790 \uc5f0\uc608\uc778 1 \uc704 \ub294\u2026 \uc288\ud37c \uc8fc\ub2c8\uc