Hyun-taek |title=\uae40\ud76c\ucca0, \uc624\ub298 \uc2e0\uace1 '\uc61b\ub0a0 \uc0ac\ub78c', \uc74c\uc6d0\u00b7MV \uacf5\uac1c |url=http://www.edaily.co.kr/news/read?newsId=01243126622459400&mediaCodeNo=258 |access-date=May 16, 2019 |work=E Daily |date=April 24, 2019 |language=ko |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424025314/http://www.edaily.co.kr/news/read?newsId=01243126622459400&mediaCodeNo=258 |archive-date=April 24, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref> It subsequently topped the charts in seven different countries.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Ahn |first1=Jin-yong |title=\uae40\ud76c\ucca0 \uc2e0\uace1 '\uc61b\ub0a0 \uc0ac\ub78c', \uc544\uc774\ud2a0\uc988 \uc2f1\uae00 \ucc28\ud2b8 \uc804 \uc138\uacc4 7\uac1c \uc9c0\uc5ed\uc11c 1\uc704 |url=http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=20190425MW161832994198 |access-date=May 16, 2019 |work=Munhwa |date=April 25, 2019 |language=ko}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Choi |first1=Young-jae |title=\uae40\ud76c\ucca0 \uccab \uc194\ub85c\uace1 \ubc1c\ud45c 7\uac1c\uad6d \ub3d9\uc2dc 1\uc704 |url=http://www.kwnews.co.kr/nview.asp?s=601&aid=219042600069 |access-date=May 16, 2019 |work=Kw News |date=April 27, 2019 |language=ko}}</ref> On May 4 and 5, Heechul held his first talk show event, which sold-out in one minute from the start of the internet ticket booking.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Jo |first1=Hyun-joo |title=\ubcf8\uaca9 \ucd94\uc5b5\uc18c\ud658\uc1fc...'\uc6b0\uc8fc \ub300\uc2a4\ud0c0' \uae40\ud76c\ucca0, \uccab \ud1a0\ud06c\uc1fc \ub9c8\ubb34\ub9ac |url=https://www.ytn.co.kr/_sn/0117_201905061704596511 |access-date=May 16, 2019 |work=YTN |date=May 6, 2019 |language=ko}}</ref> In 2019, Heechul appeared in more than ten programs over the course of the year, and became a fixed cast member of the reality program ''[[My Little Old Boy]]''<ref>{{Cite news |script-title=ko:\uae40\ud76c\ucca0, \uc5b4\uba38\ub2c8\uc640 SBS '\ubbf8\uc6b4 \uc6b0\ub9ac \uc0c8\ub07c' \ud569\ub958|url=https://www.yna.co.kr/view/AKR20190822058400005|access-